"{\"uid\": \"harrowtimes.co.uk-news-national-24020550.olympic-host-country-france-sees-less-disorder-new-years-eve\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  France saw fewer of the car burnings that usually blight the arrival of a new year as the Olympic host country celebrated the start of 2024, its interior minister said on Monday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 8, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9997330350095034, \"rank\": 0.00017255629676611175, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 380 arrests made nationwide overnight was a 10% drop compared with a year ago, said Gerald Darmanin, citing preliminary early morning figures.\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 270, \"end\": 276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"score\": 0.9995950865536521, \"rank\": 0.000359705900110608, \"text\": \"Gerald\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Authorities counted 745 vehicle fires, also 10% fewer than last year, Mr Darmanin said.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"About 40 police officers suffered slight injuries, a 40% fall on last year, he added.\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Law enforcement authorities had been eager to prove that 2024's arrival could be celebrated without a major security crisis as they gear up for the Summer Games that open in Paris on July 26.\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 680, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.359408914918082e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Authorities had vowed that New Year's Eve security would be tight across France, with 90,000 law enforcement officers deployed.\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 772, \"end\": 778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9997330350095034, \"rank\": 0.00017255629676611175, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Paris, celebrations centred on the Champs-Elysees, where the Arc de Triomphe was crowned with fireworks and bathed in lights and video projections, including of the five Olympic rings.\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 831, \"end\": 836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.359408914918082e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 866, \"end\": 880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"score\": 0.9992163039514818, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Champs-Elysees\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\"}, {\"begin\": 892, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\", \"score\": 0.9999999999929514, \"rank\": 6.986090930835581e-12, \"text\": \"Arc de Triomphe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Darmanin said the crowd there topped a million people.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1074, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The security challenge ahead of the Olympics w